column2: SELECT    p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,     (p.u-p.r) as &&&, (p.r-p.i) as &&&, (p.r-p.z) as &&&, (p.g-p.r) as &&&,    p.type as obj_ph_type, pz.z as redshift into mydb.photopeasdr7 from PhotoObj AS p    JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objid = p.objid    WHERE      pz.z BETWEEN # AND #      AND (p.u-p.r <= #)      AND (p.r-p.i <= #)      AND (p.r-p.z <= #)      AND (p.g-p.r >= (p.r-p.i) + #)      AND (p.u-p.r >= #*(p.r-p.z))
